by [webmaster](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/author/sazizul/ "Posts by webmaster")
 | Nov 24, 2019 | [Conference & Seminar](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/conference-seminar/)
, [News](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/news/)

![](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/75237389_2859227534122634_2340924276317618176_o-1080x675.jpg)

Sesi Dialog Bersama 6 orang Profesor Emeritus FABU iaitu YBhg. Prof. Emeritus Dato’ Dr. Ar Elias @ Ilias bin Salleh, YBhg. Prof. Emeritus Dato’ Ar Parid Wardi bin Sudin, YBhg. Prof. Emeritus Dr. Noor Sharipah binti Sultan Sidi, YBhg. Prof. Emeritus Dr. Ismawi bin Hj Zen, YBhg. Prof. Emeritus Dr. Mohd Ibrahim bin Seeni Mohd dan YBhg. Prof. Emeritus Sr Omar bin Munir serta 1 orang Profesor Adjung FABU iaitu YBhg. Prof. Adjung LAr. Zainul Hakim bin Mohd Zain.
